Loops:
1. while 
2. do while
3. for 
Syntax:
1. while :Entry Control loop.
	while(condition){
		Statements;
		inc/dec;
	}
2. do while : Exit control loop
	do{
		Statements;
		inc/dec;
	}while(condition);
		
3. for loop:
		for(initialization; condition; inc/dec){
			Statements;	
		}

































